data.description: Back On Market-At No Fault To The Seller! Welcome to your dream home! This 2021 built gem offers the epitome of modern living with 5 bedrooms, 4 full baths, and pristine, like-new construction. The great news is you get to choose your kids school within this sought after school district. The upstairs loft provides additional space, while the main level provides a guest suite and bathroom for added convenience. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features an oversized island and is equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a farm sink. This kitchen is a chef's delight, offering the perfect setting for creativity with an open view to the family room. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing family meals, this layout and thoughtful design make this kitchen a focal point of the home. The spacious primary suite is located upstairs. The primary bathroom is your own sanctuary. The beautiful double vanity adds a touch of elegance, providing ample space for daily routines. Pamper yourself in the large garden tub, while the separate shower provides a relaxing experience. Experience luxury with an extended covered patio overlooking a private fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or enjoying peaceful moments. Beyond the impeccable interior, this residence is located near shopping, ensuring convenience at your fingertips. Don't miss the chance to make this home yours and elevate your living experience to new heights!
